.TH "lpfc_sli4_perform_vport_cvl" 9 "lpfc_sli4_perform_vport_cvl" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
lpfc_sli4_perform_vport_cvl \- Perform clear virtual link on a vport
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "struct lpfc_nodelist *" lpfc_sli4_perform_vport_cvl
.BI "(struct lpfc_vport *vport "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "vport" 12
pointer to vport data structure.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This routine is to perform Clear Virtual Link (CVL) on a vport in
response to a CVL event.

Return the pointer to the ndlp with the vport if successful, otherwise
return NULL.
